00:22:10,775 --> 00:22:13,287
There are five humans, all male.

336
00:22:26,169 --> 00:22:27,449
One, two...

337
00:22:27,687 --> 00:22:28,616
That's four

338
00:22:28,744 --> 00:22:29,973
and five.

339
00:22:36,179 --> 00:22:39,691
So you must be Kars. You're fast.

340
00:22:39,961 --> 00:22:43,743
In just a few hours, you heard about your friend's defeat,

341
00:22:43,782 --> 00:22:45,912
learned that we had obtained the stone,

342
00:22:46,063 --> 00:22:48,740
found our location, and have come for it.

343
00:22:48,934 --> 00:22:50,478
Very impressive.

344
00:22:50,529 --> 00:22:54,181
And then this brutal, perfectly calculated assault.

345
00:22:54,219 --> 00:22:58,225
Not one of my men made even the
slightest sound before they died.

346
00:22:58,735 --> 00:23:01,856
I was sure there were only five men in this room.

347
00:23:02,676 --> 00:23:06,712
Now tell me, why can't I sense your body heat?

348
00:23:07,103 --> 00:23:08,585
Hey, rifle heads,

349
00:23:09,048 --> 00:23:11,972
what's a guy gotta do to get a little food in here?

