00:23:12,766 --> 00:23:13,678
Kars!

351
00:23:15,521 --> 00:23:16,244
Huh?

352
00:23:16,624 --> 00:23:18,293
This man's mechanical.

353
00:23:18,595 --> 00:23:19,803
Wait a minute.

354
00:23:21,744 --> 00:23:23,699
You're Von Stroheim!

355
00:23:33,389 --> 00:23:36,436
I'll be the roundabout

356
00:23:36,834 --> 00:23:40,471
the words will make you out and out

